title: Get Even RePack by BlackBox
description:
Year of manufacture: 2017 
Genre: Action, 1st Person, 3D 
Developer: The Farm 51 
Publisher: BANDAI NAMCO Entertainment 
Publication Type: RePack 
Language: RUS | ENG 
Language of voice: ENG 
Tablet: Wash (CODEX) 

SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS: 
✔ Operating system: Windows 7, 8, 10 (64-bit versions) 
✔ Processor: Intel CPU Core i5-2500K 3.3GHz / AMD CPU Phenom II X4 940 
✔ Operating system memory: 8 GB 
✔ Video card: Nvidia GPU GeForce GTX 660 / AMD GPU Radeon HD 7870 (DirectX: Version 11) 
✔ Sound Card: Sound device compatible with DirectX® 11 
✔ Free space on hard disk: 29 GB 

DESCRIPTION: 
Get Even is a first-person shooter, from the creators of Painkiller, the action of the game unfolds in the recollections of the protagonist, trying to learn more about his past. Breathe ... Remember: a girl, a chair, a bomb. Do not be afraid ... Go to the depth of the memory. Relax ... Look for memories in the dark corners of your mind. Will you find her? Time is short ... It's part of your treatment
